Author: aszlig <aszlig@nix.build>
Date:   Mon May 14 14:23:11 2018 +0200

    Properly downgrade Bootstrap to version 4.1.0
    
    Using a caret ranges will still select Bootstrap version 4.1.1, because
    it's only a minor update. We're not using package locks in our fork, so
    let's set a fixed version.
    
    Once this patch no longer applies cleanly, we can look into the changes
    and eventually drop it once upstream has fixed the issue with Bootstrap
    4.1.1.
    
    Signed-off-by: aszlig <aszlig@nix.build>
    Filename: fix-bootstrap-downgrade.patch

